Package: concstats
Title: Market structure and concentration measures
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Andreas",
           family = "Schneider",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "schneiderconsultingpy@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5630-1097"))
Description: Based on individual market shares the function calculates a set of
    different structural and concentration measures, e.g. k-firm ratios, Herfindahl-Hirschman index,
    dual of Herfindahl-Hirschman index, Stenbacka-index, Berry index, Entropy and others. The result is a vector in table format.
